#: includes/settings-page.php:584
msgid "Exclude File Extensions"
msgstr ""

#: includes/settings-page.php:588
msgid "Enter file extensions to exclude from being downloaded during Preloading. Use commas to separate each extension."
msgstr ""

#: includes/settings-page.php:589
msgid "Nginx cache is designed to cache dynamic content, such as PHP-generated pages. Static assets like CSS, JS, and images are not cached by Nginx."
